<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="#" class="navbar-brand">Travel Explorer</a>
        <button class="nav-toggle" onclick="toggleNav()">&#9776;</button>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#section1">Home</a>
            <a href="#section2">Destinations</a>
            <a href="#section3">Testimonials</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="contact-btn">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div id="progress-bar"></div>
    <div id="fullpage">
        
        <div class="section section1"> 
            <div class="card" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2>Explore the World</h2>
                <p>Discover breathtaking destinations and experience unforgettable adventures.</p>
                <a href="#section2" class="btn">Explore Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section2"> 
            <div class="card" data-aos="fade-right">
                <h2>Top Destinations</h2>
                <p>Visit stunning places and create lifelong memories.</p>
                <div class="destination-grid">
                    <div class="destination">
                        <img src="/images/maldives1.jpg" alt="Maldives">
                        <h3>Maldives</h3>
                        <p>The Maldives is a tropical paradise known for its crystal-clear waters, white sandy beaches, and luxurious resorts. It's a perfect destination for relaxation and water sports.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="destination">
                        <img src="/images/paris1.jpg" alt="Paris">
                        <h3>Paris, France</h3>
                        <p>Paris, the City of Light, is renowned for its iconic landmarks like the Eiffel Tower, the Louvre Museum, and its romantic atmosphere. It's a must-visit for culture, history, and art lovers.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="destination">
                        <img src="/images/swiss1.jpg" alt="Switzerland">
                        <h3>Swiss Alps</h3>
                        <p>The Swiss Alps offer stunning mountain scenery, world-class skiing resorts, and charming villages. Whether you're an adventure enthusiast or just looking to relax in nature, the Swiss Alps have something for everyone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section3"> 
            <div class="testimonial-slider" data-aos="fade-up">
                <h2>What Our Travelers Say</h2>
                <div class="testimonial">
                    <p>"Travel Explorer made my trip unforgettable! Everything was perfectly arranged."</p>
                    <h4>- Sarah Williams</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial">
                    <p>"Best travel experience ever! Highly recommended for adventure lovers."</p>
                    <h4>- John Smith</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

